snippet: Representative James P. Moran, Democrat of Virginia, announced on Wednesday that he would not seek re-election in November, making him the latest in a string of recent retirements in the House.
abstract: Representative James P. Moran, Democrat of Virginia, announced on Wednesday that he would not seek re-election in November, making him the latest in a string of recent retirements in the House.

headline.main: Virginia's Moran to Retire From House After 23 Years
